short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Makes the roblox audio create page better

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Introducing "[CORRUPTED]" – the ultimate audio asset management tool for Roblox Studio!

Are you tired of the uncertainty surrounding your audio uploads on Roblox? Bid farewell to guesswork with [CORRUPTED]. This indispensable Chrome extension enhances your Roblox Studio experience by integrating informative icons directly onto the audio uploading page. These icons provide instant clarity on the status of your audio assets, whether they're pending, accepted, declined, or archived.

But that's not all! [CORRUPTED] goes beyond status indicators – it introduces a groundbreaking feature: Multi-upload. Say goodbye to tedious one-by-one uploads. With [CORRUPTED]'s Multi-upload functionality, you can effortlessly upload multiple audio files simultaneously, saving precious time and turbocharging your development process.

And now, in response to user feedback, we're thrilled to announce the newest addition to [CORRUPTED]'s arsenal: Audio Download. Simply click on the icon associated with any audio file within Roblox Studio, and [CORRUPTED] will automatically download it to your desired location. No more cumbersome steps or external tools – [CORRUPTED] streamlines your workflow by putting all the essential audio management tools at your fingertips.

Whether you're a seasoned Roblox developer or a newcomer to the creative scene, [CORRUPTED] empowers you to manage audio assets with unmatched ease and precision. Elevate your Roblox Studio workflow and experience the efficiency boost you've been craving. Try [CORRUPTED] today and unlock a new level of productivity!
